name: CSSValueList
description: The CSSValueList interface derives from the CSSValue interface and provides the abstraction of an ordered collection of CSS values.

members.name: CSSValueList.length
members.description: An unsigned long representing the number of CSSValues in the list.

members.name: CSSValueList.item()
members.description: This method is used to retrieve a CSSValue by ordinal index. The order in this collection represents the order of the values in the CSS style property. If index is greater than or equal to the number of values in the list, this returns null.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: An unsigned long representing the index of the CSS value within the collection.
